    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363330/extras/970580b752162f1d0d7c9bbcd04e31b4.avif?t=1765341621\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363330/extras/a02db74b02273195225b0fdca5b3be2f.poster.avif?t=1765341621\" width=605 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363330/extras/a02db74b02273195225b0fdca5b3be2f.webm?t=1765341621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363330/extras/bb7d977755b8f598a61a3e70e646889e.avif?t=1765341621\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br>欢迎来到女巫世界，这是一款益智游戏，你可以沉浸在女巫和魔法师的神奇世界中。收集以邪恶的女巫和仁慈的女巫为主题的精美拼图，并享受将它们拼凑在一起以显示令人惊叹的图像的挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363330/extras/96644cfb0eba8b3e0e34e16a8ac73e0c.avif?t=1765341621\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>随着你在关卡中的进展，你会遇到新的和更复杂的谜题，这将考验你的技能并让你参与其中。巫师世界有各种难度的关卡和大量错综复杂的艺术品可供发现，为谜题爱好者和魔法爱好者提供了享受娱乐的机会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363330/extras/58005dbbd777bf30a2f5cdced91a081d.avif?t=1765341621\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>因此，从平凡中抽身而出，潜入《女巫世界》的巫术和阴谋的世界。今天就来收集、拼凑和揭开这个迷人的益智游戏的神秘面纱吧! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363330/extras/6001f6fb5867b3d0b54014d7c07d7a22.avif?t=1765341621\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>让迷人的图像和具有挑战性的谜题来迷惑你吧!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可爱的女巫和魔法师女孩<br></li><li> 提示<br></li><li> 拼图<br></li><li> 放松的音乐<br></li><li> 有用的热键</li></ul>",
